-709169536.text: "LPA induced a dose responsive proliferation of C6 cells after 48 h. Proliferation was blocked by inhibitors of the sodium and proton exchanger type 1 (NHE1), Rho associated kinase, the phosphatidylinositol 3-kinase/Akt pathway (PI3K and Akt), protein kinase C (PKC) and extracellular signal regulated kinase kinase (MEK)."
